{"tid":1754431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援SJ始源於twitter對香港新聞讚好而被中國網民惡意中傷一事","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T15:11:40.000Z","uid":225754,"like":181,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"c614bee26c3db07eb5b047790eb0b54b358b16ed","tid":1754431,"uid":225754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B5RbhHcBgqs/?igshid=xecqnhys1rye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB5RbhHcBgqs%2F%3Figshid%3Dxecqnhys1rye&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=6c6b5767\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB5RbhHcBgqs%2F%3Figshid%3Dxecqnhys1rye&h=aef9b471\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B5RbhHcBgqs/?igshid=xecqnhys1rye</a><br />\n<br />\n[有關聲援SJ始源/個封專輯認購因由]<br />\n<br />\nSUPER JUNIOR成員始源昨日(24日)因為在Twitter上讚好一篇韓國《朝鮮日報》有關西灣河中槍少年受訪的報導，而受到大批中國網民與粉絲攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKHnhPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKHnhPj.jpg&h=3ac2f593&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3mbVA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3mbVA1.jpg&h=581417a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中國粉絲於社交網站強烈抨擊，指責始源作為公眾人物不應接觸政治，但反而要求他為此行為道歉並作出「交代」，意圖強迫他變相表態支持其中一方，甚至要求其退出所屬團體，認為此行為會連累其隊友。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，始源對此報道<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並無任何文字回應</span></span>。香港社會運動發展已經受到國際關注，而始源只是留意相關新聞，並不代表他作出取態。另外作為擁有民主與言論自由的韓國公民，理所當然地可就任何新聞自由表態，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如何使用社交媒體亦不應因身分而受限</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我們認為始源毋需就此行為對無理取鬧並過份解讀的中國網民交代</span>，並希望始源知道香港ELF無論如何都全力支持他以及SUPER JUNIOR全體成員。我們與很多偶像的粉絲一樣，並不希望自己的偶像捲入政治表態的糾紛，更不希望偶像因為一個讚好的動作被網民惡意中傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">有見及此，我們計劃發起團購，購買始源個人封面版本的SJ專輯《Timeslip》，以實際行動支持始源。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n🌟有關活動由一眾LIHKG ELF發起<br />\n只為用行動支持始源 不賺分文<br />\n完成團購後會貼出收據證明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1JE4ok.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw1JE4ok.png&h=6f66ab0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56fac3467d78a12ef9dc4e6fd4af18b4cbf83a1a","tid":1754431,"uid":271869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdd7622ac6cc42f0d0c5c0f3b3b1e62de011540","tid":1754431,"uid":195063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"G持崔始源"},{"pid":"888604a7d2b7062120812cf1b9cfd94e2866ae1d","tid":1754431,"uid":163649,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"推啊！！自己的馬自己救！港飯企出黎啊！"},{"pid":"8be9c6694dbfe685460200733709a9daecb5d934","tid":1754431,"uid":210254,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"但係佢好似取消咗讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5a44d59cc353ee42994b10751b067d2cca3b2a","tid":1754431,"uid":263569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:06:39.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"a66f271b2f05c97d1e920d8321dcc6d0243362eb","tid":1754431,"uid":300310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g持"},{"pid":"2f42fa22142ae770b3e62796c1e432dfdee53a53","tid":1754431,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"90b5648e12c787cdc856f61a1b41327d87949338","tid":1754431,"uid":6156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit